52:52.000 --> 53:01.000
Destination weddings

53:01.000 --> 53:09.000
A destination wedding or a wedding moon from wedding and honeymoon.

53:09.000 --> 53:13.000
A wedding is away from your home.

53:13.000 --> 53:19.000
Traditionally, weddings often happen in the bride's town.

53:19.000 --> 53:25.000
But you can go to a different town or a different country.

53:25.000 --> 53:29.000
And these days, some people do that.

53:29.000 --> 53:38.000
About one couple in ones from the UK goes to a different country for their wedding.

53:38.000 --> 53:47.000
And about one couple in five in the USA has a wedding away from home.

53:47.000 --> 53:51.000
Many famous people have destination weddings.

53:51.000 --> 53:59.000
Fish and tall crews and kooky homes had their wedding in Italy.

53:59.000 --> 54:08.000
David Beckham and Victoria Adams got married in a Carmel, Ireland.

54:08.000 --> 54:17.000
And Ben Affleck and Jennifer Garner got to an island in the Caribbean.

54:17.000 --> 54:21.000
Why have a destination wedding?

54:21.000 --> 54:24.000
There are many reasons.

54:24.000 --> 54:28.000
Here are some of them.

54:28.000 --> 54:36.000
When the bride comes from one country and the groom from a different one,

54:36.000 --> 54:44.000
sometimes it is easier to have the wedding in a third country.

54:44.000 --> 54:47.000
It is unusual.

54:47.000 --> 54:54.000
Some couples do not want to be the same as their friends.

54:54.000 --> 55:00.000
Lots of people think differently about a wedding too.

55:00.000 --> 55:10.000
Sometimes the bride's parents, the groom's parents, friends, brothers and sisters

55:10.000 --> 55:15.000
all want to do different things.

55:15.000 --> 55:21.000
With a destination wedding, it is your wedding.

55:21.000 --> 55:26.000
Perhaps you do not want a traditional wedding.

55:26.000 --> 55:31.000
With church, flowers and bridesmaids.

55:31.000 --> 55:42.000
A destination wedding can be a ceremony by the sea, on a mountain, in a castle.

55:42.000 --> 55:52.000
It can have thirty guests or just six or no guests at all.

55:52.000 --> 55:58.000
It can be smaller and cheaper and cheaper, of course.

55:58.000 --> 56:02.000
It will not chop her for the guests' guests.

56:02.000 --> 56:08.000
But it is for the bride or the groom.

56:08.000 --> 56:16.000
Some couples from colder countries are interested in a destination wedding

56:16.000 --> 56:20.000
because they want a sunny day.

56:20.000 --> 56:28.000
So they go to a Greek island or to the Caribbean.

56:28.000 --> 56:36.000
In popular places like Hawaii, couples can pay for a wedding planner.

56:36.000 --> 56:41.000
This person arranges everything for the wedding.

56:41.000 --> 56:45.000
